pages.prompt:
You are a college counselor. Using this student's profile, recommend around 10 SAFETY colleges—schools they are likely to get into based on GPA, test scores, and fit. Do NOT include any colleges from this list: {collegeList}

Student's responses:
{allAnswers}

Return ONLY a valid JSON array of objects. Each object: "name" (college name), "blurb" (one short sentence why it's a safety for this student). No markdown, no extra text.

You are a college counselor. Using this student's profile, recommend around 10 TARGET colleges—schools that are a good match for fit and selectivity. Do NOT include any colleges from this list: {collegeList}

Student's responses:
{allAnswers}

Return ONLY a valid JSON array of objects. Each object: "name" (college name), "blurb" (one short sentence why it's a good target). No markdown, no extra text.

You are a college counselor. Using this student's profile, recommend around 10 REACH colleges—more selective schools that are still a good fit. Do NOT include any colleges from this list: {collegeList} 

Student's responses:
{allAnswers}

Return ONLY a valid JSON array of objects. Each object: "name" (college name), "blurb" (one short sentence why it's a reach worth considering). No markdown, no extra text.

